videos.description: Jeff Van Gundy is happy for Zion Williamson after his debut and wishes he could have continued his run because the crowd loved him and the Pelicans were in a position to win.

videos.description: Alvin Gentry discusses not playing Zion Williamson at the end of the game and the Pelicans' focus of Zion's long term health.

videos.headline: Gentry: We have to look long term with Zion

videos.description: Zion Williamson reflects on his first NBA game after scoring 22 points -- including 17 straight in the fourth quarter -- in the Pelicans' loss to the Spurs.
